spirit:component.spirit:name: Convolution_Controller_axi_hbicap_0_1

spirit:addressBlock.spirit:name: Mem0
spirit:addressBlock.spirit:description: AXI MM Memory space for burst writing/reading to/from the ICAP

spirit:addressBlock.spirit:name: Reg0
spirit:addressBlock.spirit:description: AXI lite register space for the ICAP

spirit:field.spirit:name: size
spirit:field.spirit:description: Number of words to be transferred to/from the ICAPEn from/to the FIFO

spirit:field.spirit:name: read
spirit:field.spirit:description: 1 = Initiates read back from ICAPEn to Read FIFO Self Clear

spirit:component.spirit:description: This core enables an embedded microprocessor, such as the MicroBlaze processor, to read and write the Field Programmable Gate Array (FPGA) configuration memory through the Internal Configuration Access Port (ICAPEn).

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_READ_PATH
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Select the interface type for the read data.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_WRITE_FIFO_DEPTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Select the depth of the Write FIFO.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_READ_FIFO_DEPTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Select the depth of the Read FIFO.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_ICAP_DWIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Select the data width of ICAPEn. Valid values are 8, 16 and 32.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_BRAM_SRL_FIFO_TYPE
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Select the type of FIFOs to be used. One can choose between Block RAM and Distributed RAM FIFOs.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_ICAP_EXTERNAL
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: Use ICAP external to the IP
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Accessing the externally shared ICAP primitive

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_SHARED_STARTUP
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: ENabling this will bring the unused startup pins to outside.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_NOREAD
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Not instantiating the Read FIFO further reduces the resource utilization. No data can be read from ICAPEn.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_MODE
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Not instantiating the Write FIFO will reduce the resource utilization.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_INCLUDE_STARTUP
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: EOS signal output from the STARTUPEn primitive is used to control the access to ICAPEn.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_ENABLE_ASYNC
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Select this when ICAP_Clk and S_AXI_ACLK are different.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_OPERATION
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Select this to read large frames of data from the ICAPEn

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: S_AXI_AWUSER_WIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: AXI Datapath AW User Width (in bits)

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: S_AXI_WUSER_WIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: AXI Datapath W User Width (in bits)

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: S_AXI_BUSER_WIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: AXI Datapath B User Width (in bits)

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: S_AXI_ARUSER_WIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: AXI Datapath AR User Width (in bits)

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: S_AXI_RUSER_WIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: AXI Datapath R User Width (in bits)

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_READ_DELAY
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Configure additional read delay for valid data from ICAPEn.
